snippet.title: MoonBase Commander: Official Launch Trailer - Out Now on Steam
snippet.description:
MoonBase Commander is available now on Steam: http://goo.gl/yzjk94 
and on the Rebellion Gamestore: http://goo.gl/wBpcJa

Moonbase Commander Official Trailer:
Jump into MoonBase Commander with our official tutorial video - death to game manuals! 
Get the edge in this turn-based strategy classic and lord it over your friends in LAN battles.
